y^{\prime}=\frac{x^{2}}{2}+x+C_{1} ; \frac{d y}{d x}=\frac{x^{2}}{2}+x+C_{1}, d y=\left(\frac{x^{2}}{2}+x+C_{1}\right) d x \\
y=\frac{x^{3}}{6}+\frac{x^{2}}{2}+C_{1} x+C_{2}
